# Title: PowerShell Script Change Permission Via Set-Acl - PsScript
# Author: frack113, Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-07-18
# Level: low
# Description: Detects PowerShell scripts set ACL to of a file or a folder
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1222
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_set_acl.yml

ScriptBlockText="*Set-Acl *" ScriptBlockText="*-AclObject *" ScriptBlockText="*-Path *"